{"comments":"Surface - material surface appearance compound.\n\nDescribes how light interacts with a surface, determining its visual\nappearance. Used for PBR (Physically Based Rendering) workflows and\nUI material design.\n\n## Surface Types\n\n- **Matte**: No reflectivity, diffuse only (paper, cloth)\n- **Glossy**: High reflectivity, specular highlight (plastic, wet paint)\n- **Metallic**: Metal-like reflection, colored specular (gold, chrome)\n- **Satin**: Soft sheen, between matte and glossy (silk, brushed metal)\n- **Textured**: Surface with tactile/visual texture (leather, concrete)\n\n## PBR Parameters\n\n- Roughness: 0.0 (mirror) to 1.0 (fully diffuse)\n- Metalness: 0.0 (dielectric) to 1.0 (metal)\n- Reflectivity: Base reflectivity at normal incidence\n\n## Dependencies\n\n- Hydrogen.Schema.Bounded\n","declarations":[{"children":[{"comments":null,"info":{"arguments":[],"declType":"dataConstructor"},"sourceSpan":{"end":[83,10],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Surface/Surface.purs","start":[83,3]},"title":"Matte"},{"comments":null,"info":{"arguments":[],"declType":"dataConstructor"},"sourceSpan":{"end":[84,11],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Surface/Surface.purs","start":[84,3]},"title":"Glossy"},{"comments":null,"info":{"arguments":[],"declType":"dataConstructor"},"sourceSpan":{"end":[85,13],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Surface/Surface.purs","start":[85,3]},"title":"Metallic"},{"comments":null,"info":{"arguments":[],"declType":"dataConstructor"},"sourceSpan":{"end":[86,10],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Surface/Surface.purs","start":[86,3]},"title":"Satin"},{"comments":null,"info":{"arguments":[],"declType":"dataConstructor"},"sourceSpan":{"end":[87,13],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Surface/Surface.purs","start":[87,3]},"title":"Textured"},{"comments":null,"info":{"arguments":[],"declType":"dataConstructor"},"sourceSpan":{"end":[88,11],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Surface/Surface.purs",